Kau dah beritahu Tonfah?

778
00:59:46,819 --> 00:59:47,688
Pasal move on tu?

779
00:59:48,352 --> 00:59:50,247
Belum lagi.

780
00:59:50,954 --> 00:59:51,805
Kau masih nak beritahu dia?

781
00:59:52,520 --> 00:59:53,500
Mungkin kau tak perlu pun.

782
00:59:54,885 --> 00:59:55,718
Jo.

783
00:59:56,185 --> 00:59:57,576
Tapi kali ni aku serius.

784
00:59:58,343 --> 01:00:00,020
Aku betul-betul nak move on.

785
01:00:00,893 --> 01:00:03,047
Selain peluk, apa lagi kau buat?

786
01:00:04,783 --> 01:00:05,694
Kau cakaplah.

787
01:00:06,223 --> 01:00:06,914
Korang tidur sekali?

788
01:00:07,567 --> 01:00:08,896
Apa benda, Jo?

789
01:00:09,186 --> 01:00:10,804
Ala, kalau kau, memang boleh jadi.

790
01:00:11,162 --> 01:00:13,543
- Kau ingat aku orang macam mana?
- Menyampah.

791
01:00:17,760 --> 01:00:18,330
Err...

792
01:00:20,773 --> 01:00:22,293
Dia tak sihat.

793
01:00:23,080 --> 01:00:24,019
Aku takut dia mati.

794
01:00:24,805 --> 01:00:25,983
Jadi aku

795
01:00:27,721 --> 01:00:29,060
jaga dia sikit.

796
01:00:29,922 --> 01:00:32,408
Aku cuma tak nak ada hantu sebelah lagi, itu je.

797
01:00:33,552 --> 01:00:35,487
Aku tak sangka ini cara orang "move on."

798
01:00:36,222 --> 01:00:36,711
Nampak?

799
01:00:37,392 --> 01:00:39,494
Aku cerita semua, kau tetap usik aku macam ni.

800
01:00:39,610 --> 01:00:40,908
Kau bercanggah dengan diri sendiri.

801
01:00:46,706 --> 01:00:48,591
Benda macam ni ambil masa, kan?

802
01:00:49,841 --> 01:00:52,783
Apa-apa je. Ambil seumur hidup pun tak apa.

803
01:00:54,521 --> 01:00:55,668
Ya, aku tahu.

804
01:00:56,539 --> 01:00:57,881
Aku takkan ambil seumur hidup pun.

805
01:01:00,534 --> 01:01:01,093
Rasanya.

806
01:01:05,928 --> 01:01:07,730
Helo, Khun Phuangthong.

807
01:01:08,582 --> 01:01:10,242
Saya rasa ada hantu kacau saya.

808
01:01:11,160 --> 01:01:12,047
Hantu dalam bilik awak?

809
01:01:12,866 --> 01:01:13,545
Siapa yang buat?

810
01:01:14,097 --> 01:01:15,185
Dia buat apa pada awak?

811
01:01:15,856 --> 01:01:18,162
Saya tak tahu siapa.

812
01:01:18,690 --> 01:01:19,734
Rasa macam lemas.

813
01:01:20,918 --> 01:01:21,946
Macam ada yang peluk saya.

814
01:01:23,272 --> 01:01:24,502
Itu memang menakutkan.

815
01:01:25,019 --> 01:01:26,875
Awak ada buat apa-apa pada mereka?

816
01:01:28,065 --> 01:01:29,131
Tak.

817
01:01:29,788 --> 01:01:31,752
Saya pun dah berhari-hari tak masuk bilik.

818
01:01:31,985 --> 01:01:34,425
Sebelum ni semuanya okey je.

819
01:01:35,177 --> 01:01:37,671
Atau mungkin mereka marah sebab kita tak buat merit.

820
01:01:38,133 --> 01:01:40,389
Baik, saya akan buat merit untuk mereka.

821
01:01:40,777 --> 01:01:42,764
Saya pun nak pergi kuil juga.

822
01:01:43,413 --> 01:01:44,152
Mm.

823
01:01:44,854 --> 01:01:46,831
Tolong buatkan untuk saya, Khun Phuangthong.

824
01:01:48,035 --> 01:01:48,687
Mm.

825
01:01:49,320 --> 01:01:50,765
Beritahu saya kalau ada apa-apa jadi.

826
01:01:51,328 --> 01:01:52,802
Jaga diri.

827
01:01:54,078 --> 01:01:55,460
Ya, Khun Phuangthong.

828
01:01:56,077 --> 01:01:58,186
Hari ni hari pertama semester saya.

829
01:01:58,542 --> 01:02:00,644
Boleh beri saya berkat?

830
01:02:01,102 --> 01:02:02,177
Semoga berjaya, sayang.

831
01:02:02,610 --> 01:02:04,237
Saya harap awak jumpa perkara yang baik saja.

832
01:02:04,721 --> 01:02:07,388
Semoga hari ini jadi hari yang baik untuk awak.

833
01:02:07,758 --> 01:02:08,645
Terima kasih.

834
01:02:13,007 --> 01:02:14,802
Itu saja dulu, Khun Phuangthong.

835
01:02:26,085 --> 01:02:26,791
Nak pergi kelas?

836
01:02:27,582 --> 01:02:28,158
Ya.

837
01:02:29,920 --> 01:02:30,748
Jadi,

838
01:02:31,367 --> 01:02:32,337
Selsema dah baik?

839
01:02:34,080 --> 01:02:36,260
Terima kasih lap badan aku.

840
01:02:38,842 --> 01:02:39,431
Ya.

841
01:02:41,974 --> 01:02:43,050
Kau nak pergi macam mana?

842
01:02:44,317 --> 01:02:45,165
Naik motor?

843
01:02:55,232 --> 01:02:55,767
Tunggu.

844
01:02:57,277 --> 01:02:58,202
Err—

845
01:02:59,108 --> 01:03:00,044
Aku hantar kau.

846
01:03:00,934 --> 01:03:03,651
Kau baru baik. Jangan naik motor.

847
01:03:05,400 --> 01:03:06,192
Tak apa.

848
01:03:07,561 --> 01:03:08,250
Aku hantar kau.

849
01:03:58,048 --> 01:03:59,280
Hei, kau belajar kat mana tadi?

850
01:04:00,254 --> 01:04:01,622
Fakulti Sains.

851
01:04:02,420 --> 01:04:03,577
Apa kau cakap?

852
01:04:04,801 --> 01:04:05,697
Sains.

853
01:04:09,885 --> 01:04:11,502
Cakap kuat sikit.

854
01:04:16,019 --> 01:04:16,902
Sains.

855
01:04:19,774 --> 01:04:20,318
Ha.

856
01:04:52,361 --> 01:04:54,071
Kau peluk aku kuat. Takut?

857
01:04:54,591 --> 01:04:55,525
Sikit.

858
01:04:56,280 --> 01:04:57,402
Aku jarang naik belakang motor.

859
01:04:58,002 --> 01:04:58,462
Oh?

860
01:05:00,822 --> 01:05:01,515
Mm.

861
01:05:20,096 --> 01:05:20,955
Terima kasih.

862
01:05:24,770 --> 01:05:25,703
Pukul berapa kau habis?

863
01:05:26,845 --> 01:05:27,440
5 petang.

864
01:05:28,982 --> 01:05:29,912
Lepas tu kau tunggu sini.

865
01:05:31,773 --> 01:05:32,506
Kau nak ambil aku?

866
01:05:33,585 --> 01:05:36,284
Aku hantar kau. Macam mana lagi kau nak balik?

867
01:05:37,722 --> 01:05:39,749
- Aku boleh jalan.
- Kau bergurau?

868
01:05:40,693 --> 01:05:41,600
Aku tunggu sini.

869
01:05:46,297 --> 01:05:47,459
Terima kasih tumpangkan.

870
01:05:51,733 --> 01:05:52,774
Cakap macam betul-betul ikhlas.

871
01:05:56,244 --> 01:05:57,475
Memang ikhlas.

872
01:05:59,072 --> 01:06:00,736
Cakap "terima kasih" elok-elok.

873
01:06:03,768 --> 01:06:04,345
Cakap.

874
01:06:07,466 --> 01:06:08,410
Terima kasih.

875
01:06:10,091 --> 01:06:11,613
Sebut nama aku sekali.

876
01:06:13,457 --> 01:06:15,254
Terima kasih tumpangkan.

877
01:06:16,958 --> 01:06:17,588
P’Arthit.

878
01:06:40,992 --> 01:06:42,248
Aku dah suka seseorang.

879
01:06:42,365 --> 01:06:44,560
- Aku cuba nak pikat dia.
- Bukan senang, P’.

880
01:06:44,684 --> 01:06:46,133
Kalau kau nak pikat dia,

881
01:06:46,333 --> 01:06:47,571
apa yang susah sangat?

882
01:06:47,780 --> 01:06:50,265
Jadi diri sendiri. Ikhlas. Natural.

883
01:06:50,616 --> 01:06:52,081
Aku akan pecahkan pintu betul-betul.

884
01:06:53,194 --> 01:06:56,657
Mungkin jangan jadi diri sendiri.
Jadi sikit lebih baik, cukup.

885
01:06:56,823 --> 01:06:59,665
Sejak aku pikat kau, berapa mata aku dapat?

886
01:06:59,721 --> 01:07:00,589
Kosong.

887
01:07:00,899 --> 01:07:02,078
Kenapa kau suka aku?

888
01:07:02,277 --> 01:07:03,866
Soalan tu aku pun tak tahu.

889
01:07:03,921 --> 01:07:05,182
Aku cuma tahu mesti kau.

890
01:07:05,552 --> 01:07:07,408
Okey, kosong—daripada langsung tak ada.

891
01:07:08,305 --> 01:07:10,250
Mulai sekarang, aku mula kira.

